the grain reserves.

844
01:23:42,600 --> 01:23:44,434
GAlUS: This can't be true.

845
01:23:45,019 --> 01:23:47,521
LUClLLA: He's selling
Rome's reserves of grain.

846
01:23:48,106 --> 01:23:51,024
