01:32:37,620 --> 01:32:40,205
CROWD: (CHANTlNG) Kill! Kill! Kill!

959
01:32:44,085 --> 01:32:45,669
Stay close.

960
01:32:48,172 --> 01:32:49,714
(CROWD CHEERlNG)

961
01:32:51,634 --> 01:32:53,510
Come together!

