975
01:34:07,418 --> 01:34:08,501
(GRUNTlNG)

976
01:34:10,129 --> 01:34:11,254
(GROANS)

977
01:34:12,298 --> 01:34:13,965
(CROWD CHEERlNG)

978
01:34:15,259 --> 01:34:16,509
Hagen!

979
01:34:17,553 --> 01:34:19,137
(CROWD ROARlNG)

980
01:34:40,660 --> 01:34:44,162
This column to the chariot!
This column stay with me!

981
01:34:47,833 --> 01:34:49,167
MAXlMUS: Quickly!

982
01:34:49,835 --> 01:34:52,587
